name: Clowncoin
description: Clowncoin was fair launched in May 2022 with only 1 BNB in liquidity. Ownership was renounced and LP was locked at launch. Clowncoin has a 10% buy sell tax with 5% reflections 5% LP. The Clowncoin team and community is made entirely of volunteers who work to build their own investment. There is no marketing or team wallet, holders are encouraged to help promote the project to keep the project community run.Clowncoin is on almost all major social media platforms, and has even partnered with musical artists to create original Clowncoin music videos that can be found on our YouTube and TikTok. Eventually, Clowncoin wishes to partner with celebrities and influencers to raffle off celebrity and influencer donated items. All proceeds from the raffles will be donated to charitable causes selected by the Clowncoin community. Clowns are known for joy and healing.Clowncoin has already been listed on several crypto tracking websites to include Moonscan, CoinPaprika, and Memetools.
